APP:
\va vittaṃ \msNKA12\msNC45\msNK28\msNK82pc\msNKo77\msGP74; vittāṃ \msNK82ac, vittas \msGP74
          \vb sa tasyehānusārataḥ \msNC45\msNKA12\msNK82\msGP43\msE;
              tattasyehānusārataḥ \msNK28, °sa tasyehanubhāyataḥ \msNKo77, tasya hānurasarataḥ \msGP74

TR:
The assistance intended only for the renunciants, [consisting of the provision of] shoes, parasols, undergarments, beds, covers and seats, oils for the feet, collyria,
          unguents, baths, food, and medicine; cleaning and painting the monastery; the recitation of the manuscript of Śiva, accompanied by [offerings of] lamps, fire,
          water, flowers;
